  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1032053/" class="title-link">“大家写给大家看的历史”？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1032053"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1091429/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1091429/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">[已注销]</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2006-03-17"
      class="main-meta">2006-03-17 22:32:37</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1032053_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  也许因为这本书原本就是在中央高级党校所作学术讲演的记录稿，全书贯穿了“阶级斗争”观念和历史观，请大家做好心理准备。不管怎么说，薄薄的小册子，还是挺好读的。另外，书中对于明末时期，中国、朝鲜和日本之间关系的文字，让人不由生出“历史总是惊人相似”的感触。

